                <note rend="inline" type="source">856d.6363/507: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in the Netherlands</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Norweb</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">The Hague</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-02-08T16:00:00+00:19">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 8, 1928—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received February 8—12:50 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>7. My telegram No. 6, February 4, 5 p.m. Am gratified to report Koloniale oil
                    bill approved this afternoon by the first chamber without record vote.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Norweb</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
